rule.sfwMessage: You Cannot Proceed Further With The Application. Please Contact NDPERS. - The SMTP host was not specified.

query.sfwSql: SELECT isnull(PA.FIRST_NAME,'')+' '+isnull(PA.MIDDLE_NAME,'') +' '+isnull(PA.LAST_NAME,'') AS FULL_NAME, P.PLAN_NAME,WBA.* FROM SGT_WSS_BEN_APP WBA WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN P WITH(NOLOCK) ON P.PLAN_ID = WBA.PLAN_ID Inner Join SGT_PERSON PA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ID = WBA.PERSON_ID

SELECT CV.CODE_VALUE, CV.[DESCRIPTION] FROM SGT_BENEFIT_PROVISION_BENEFIT_OPTION BO WITH(NOLOCK) JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON BO.BENEFIT_OPTION_ID = CV.CODE_ID AND BO.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE WHERE BO.BENEFIT_PROVISION_ID = @BENEFITPROVISIONID AND BO.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = @BENACTVALUE AND BO.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @EFFECTIVEDATE AND CASE WHEN @MARRIED = '1' THEN MARRIED ELSE SINGLE END = '1' ORDER BY BO.EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PAD.PERSON_DEPENDENT_ID AS target_person_dependent_id, CASE WHEN P.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN PD.FIRST_NAME ELSE P.FIRST_NAME END AS FIRST_NAME ,CASE WHEN P.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN PD.MIDDLE_NAME ELSE P.MIDDLE_NAME END AS MIDDLE_NAME ,CASE WHEN P.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN PD.LAST_NAME ELSE P.LAST_NAME END AS LAST_NAME ,PD.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE ,CV.[DESCRIPTION] AS RELATIONSHIP_DESCRIPTION ,PD.GENDER_VALUE ,PD.FULL_TIME_STUDENT_FLAG ,PD.MARITAL_STATUS_VALUE ,SUM(CASE WHEN PA.PLAN_ID = 12 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS is_health_enrolled_already ,SUM(CASE WHEN PA.PLAN_ID = 16 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS is_dental_enrolled_already ,SUM(CASE WHEN PA.PLAN_ID = 17 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS is_vision_enrolled_already FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEPENDENT PAD WITH(NOLOCK) JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PAD.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (@TERMINATION_DATE BETWEEN PAD.[START_DATE] AND ISNULL(PAD.END_DATE, '01/01/2900')) JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV GHDV WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY GHDVH WITH(NOLOCK) ON GHDVH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = GHDV.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID AND GHDVH.[START_DATE] <> ISNULL(GHDVH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND (@TERMINATION_DATE BETWEEN GHDVH.[START_DATE] AND ISNULL(GHDVH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900')) AND GHDVH.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' JOIN SGT_PERSON_DEPENDENT PD WITH(NOLOCK) ON PD.PERSON_DEPENDENT_ID = PAD.PERSON_DEPENDENT_ID JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV WITH(NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID = PD.RELATIONSHIP_ID AND CV.CODE_VALUE = PD.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON P WITH(NOLOCK) ON PD.DEPENDENT_PERSLINK_ID = P.PERSON_ID GROUP BY PAD.PERSON_DEPENDENT_ID, CASE WHEN P.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN PD.FIRST_NAME ELSE P.FIRST_NAME END ,CASE WHEN P.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN PD.MIDDLE_NAME ELSE P.MIDDLE_NAME END ,CASE WHEN P.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN PD.LAST_NAME ELSE P.LAST_NAME END ,PD.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE ,CV.[DESCRIPTION] ,PD.GENDER_VALUE ,PD.FULL_TIME_STUDENT_FLAG ,PD.MARITAL_STATUS_VALUE
) AS NONRETIREE_DEPS

SELECT R.PLAN_ID, D.* FROM SGT_WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST R WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_WSS_PERSON_DEPENDENT D WITH(NOLOCK) ON D.WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST_ID = R.WSS_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ENROLLMENT_REQUEST_ID WHERE WSS_BEN_APP_ID = @WSSBENAPPID AND R.PLAN_ID IN (12, 16, 17)

SELECT CODE_ID, CODE_VALUE, (CASE WHEN CODE_VALUE = 'ENRL' THEN 'I elect To continue my Group Life Insurance' ELSE 'I elect NOT to continue my Group Life Insurance' END)AS DESCRIPTION FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE CODE_ID = 6003 AND DATA1 = 'Y'
SELECT * FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WHERE CODE_ID = 2214 AND CODE_VALUE In('ALOT', 'DLOT', 'PROT')
